<p><%= @meal.proteins - Meal.min_protein_meal.proteins %> grams of extra Protein!</p>
<% if (@meal.proteins - Meal.min_protein_meal.proteins) > 100 %>
  <p>Wow! That's the equivalent of 16 ozs of Salmon!</p>
<% elsif (@meal.proteins - Meal.min_protein_meal.proteins) > 60 %>
  <p>Wow! That's the equivalent of 2 big scoops of Protein Powder!</p>
<% elsif (@meal.proteins - Meal.min_protein_meal.proteins) > 40 %>
  <p>Wow! That's the equivalent of 6 ozs of Chicken Breast!</p>
<% elsif (@meal.proteins - Meal.min_protein_meal.proteins) > 20 %>
  <p>Wow! That's the equivalent of 4 whole eggs!</p>
<% elsif (@meal.proteins - Meal.min_protein_meal.proteins) > 10 %>
  <p>Wow! That's the equivalent of 1 whole Greek Yogurt!</p>
<% end %>
<p><%= Meal.max_fat_meal.fat - @meal.fat %> grams of Fat saved!</p>
<% if (Meal.max_fat_meal.fat - @meal.fat) > 100 %>
  <p>Wow! That's the equivalent of one whole stick of butter!</p>
<% elsif (Meal.max_fat_meal.fat - @meal.fat) > 50 %>
  <p>Wow! That's the equivalent of one whole cheese pizza!</p>
<% elsif (Meal.max_fat_meal.fat - @meal.fat) > 10 %>
  <p>Wow! That's the equivalent of a pack of sliced cheese!</p>
<% end %>
